Suitable for all Oral-B Round head electric toothbrush.

Fully sealed and waterproof design, this Oral-B Electric toothbrush charger is made of insulated ABS material, IP67 grade waterproof and dust-proof. Easy to clean and it can be used in the bathroom and other humid environments. If it drops into the water and it won't be damaged and still works.

Electric toothbrush charger is very easy to use and has an inductive charging function. You put it down and charge it, pick it up and turn it off automatically. You can rest assured that charging your automatic toothbrush is safe and conc.
